data.description: Welcome to this recently renovated, move in ready gem located in the Hillsdale subdivision! Boasting 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and a plethora of recent upgrades, this residence is ready to embrace its new owner. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by the open living area with easy access to the kitchen. Experience the seamless and open single-story floorplan, thoughtfully designed to provide a spacious and unencumbered living experience. Enjoy the generous lot size, offering ample space for outdoor activities and the added convenience of RV access, perfect for storing your RV, boat or trailer with ease. Don't miss out on this opportunity! Schedule a viewing of this home before it's gone. Seller is willing to offer concessions for either a rate buydown or closing costs! Property is also eligible for up to $17,500 in Grant Money for Qualified Buyers.
